{"word":"Beth-El","slug":"beth-el","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Beth-El</b> <a href=\"#/H1008\">H1008</a> <br/> 1. A city north of Jerusalem<br/> - The ancient city adjacent to, and finally embraced in, was called Luz<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=13'>Jos 18:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=26'>Jdg 1:26</a> <br/> - Abraham establishes an altar at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=8'>Gen 12:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=13&verse=4'>Gen 13:4</a> <br/> - The place where Jacob saw the vision of the ladder<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=22'>Gen 28:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=13'>Gen 31:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=12&verse=4'>Hos 12:4</a> <br/> - Jacob builds an altar at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=15'>Gen 35:15</a> <br/> - Deborah dies at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=8'>Gen 35:8</a> <br/> - Conquered by Joshua<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=8&verse=17'>Jos 8:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=12&verse=16'>Jos 12:16</a> <br/> - Conquered by the house of Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=26'>Jdg 1:26</a> <br/> - Allotted to Benjamin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=13'>Jos 18:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=22'>Jos 18:22</a> <br/> - Court of justice held at, by Deborah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=4&verse=5'>Jdg 4:5</a> <br/> - Court of justice held at, by Samuel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=16'>1Sa 7:16</a> <br/> - Tabernacle at, and called House of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=20&verse=18'>Jdg 20:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=20&verse=31'>Jdg 20:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=21&verse=2'>Jdg 21:2</a> <br/> - Jeroboam institutes idolatrous worship at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=33'>1Ki 12:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=29'>2Ki 10:29</a> <br/> - Idolatry at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=13'>Jer 48:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=4&verse=4'>Amo 4:4</a> <br/> - Shalmanezer sends a priest to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=28'>2Ki 17:28</a> <br/> - Prophecies against the idolatrous altars at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=13&verse=6'>1Ki 13:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=13&verse=32'>1Ki 13:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=4'>2Ki 23:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=20'>2Ki 23:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=3&verse=14'>Amo 3:14</a> <br/> - The school of prophets at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=3'>2Ki 2:3</a> <br/> - Children of the school of prophets mock Elisha<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=24'>2Ki 2:24</a> <br/> - People of, return from Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=28'>Ezr 2:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=32'>Neh 7:32</a> <br/> - Prophecies against<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=5&verse=5'>Amo 5:5</a> <br/> 2. A city in the south of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=30&verse=27'>1Sa 30:27</a><br/> 3. A mountain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=2'>1Sa 13:2</a>"}]}